episodes.title: Former JW elder, now an author and pastor, tells what opened his eyes
episodes.description:
David A. Reed was a faithful JW teaching elder for many years until something happened at an annual JW summer convention that would transform the lives of both him and his wife, Penni, ultimately leading them out of the organization.

David, now an established author and a pastor in Massachusetts, has a website where you can learn more about his remarkable journey to freedom in Jesus and see a list of his books on:

http://answerjw.com/
